    Sensor_water_Aqara_text_5:
      "Dust and water resistance: the sensor meets IP67 standard, ensuring uninterrupted operation even in humid environments.",
    Sensor_water_Aqara_text_6: "Long operation: the battery provides up to 2 years of autonomous operation.",
    Sensor_gas_Aqara_text:
      "The Aqara Smart Natural Gas Detector records gas leaks, triggers an alarm, and sends a push notification to your smartphone. It connects to the 220‚ÄØV mains. The sensor includes a powerful 85‚ÄØdB siren which activates upon leak detection. A flashing red LED also turns on. When leakage is detected, it triggers sirens on all hubs. A push notification is sent to the smartphone.",
    Sensor_gas_Smartlife_text:
      "The primary purpose of this sensor is to detect gas leaks at an early stage and trigger smart home scenarios to prevent consequences of leakage.",
    Sensor_gas_metan_text_1:
      "The gas sensor is intended to alert to increased concentration of household gas (methane) in the air. The sensor operates via ZigBee wireless technology.",
