      "The gas sensor is designed to alert on increased propane concentration in the air. Housing material: ABS+PC plastic. Indicator present: yes ‚Äî red / green / yellow. The device operates only on AC power. Suitable for residential and office use.",
    Sensor_smoke_Smartlife_text:
      "Quick to respond to smoke. Thanks to high sensitivity (0.089‚Äë0.25‚ÄØdB/m), the sensor will timely detect a fire source and issue an audible alarm. Configure notifications in the ‚ÄúHome with Alice‚Äù mobile app and receive push alerts when smoke is detected. Long battery life. The sensor operates via the Zigbee wireless protocol and consumes power only when triggered and sending alerts. Easy to install ‚Äî attached with adhesive backing.",
    Sensor_smoke_Aqara_text:
      "The Aqara Smart Smoke Detector is a smart smoke sensor ‚Äî it detects smoke, activates an alarm, and sends a push notification to your smartphone. Operated by a CR17450 battery. The sensor includes a powerful 90‚ÄØdB siren which triggers when smoke is detected. A flashing red LED also activates. All smoke sensors are automatically linked. For example, if you have sensors in every room, when one detects smoke, the alarm will trigger on all sensors automatically. In this way, sensors ‚Äúback up‚Äù each other. The smoke sensor has a record autonomy ‚Äî up to 10 years on one battery.",
